Class Summary
Action Called whenever an ACTION is sent from a user.
Action.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
ChannelInfo After calling the listChannels() method in PircBotX, the server will start to send us information about each channel on the server.
ChannelInfo.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Connect This method is called once the PircBotX has successfully connected to the IRC server.
Connect.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Deop Called when a user (possibly us) gets operator status taken away.
Deop.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
DeVoice Called when a user (possibly us) gets voice status removed.
DeVoice.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Disconnect This method carries out the actions to be performed when the PircBotX gets disconnected.
Disconnect.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
FileTransferFinished This method gets called when a DccFileTransfer has finished.
FileTransferFinished.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Finger This method is called whenever we receive a FINGER request.
Finger.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
IncomingChatRequest This method will be called whenever a DCC Chat request is received.
IncomingChatRequest.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
IncomingFileTransfer This method is called whenever a DCC SEND request is sent to the PircBotX.
IncomingFileTransfer.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Invite Called when we are invited to a channel by a user.
Invite.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Join This method is called whenever someone (possibly us) joins a channel which we are on.
Join.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Kick This method is called whenever someone (possibly us) is kicked from any of the channels that we are in.
Kick.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Message Used whenever a message is sent to a channel.
Message.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Mode Used when the mode of a channel is set.
Mode.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Motd  
Motd.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
NickChange This method is called whenever someone (possibly us) changes nick on any of the channels that we are on.
NickChange.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Notice This method is called whenever we receive a notice.
Notice.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Op Called when a user (possibly us) gets granted operator status for a channel.
Op.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Part This method is called whenever someone (possibly us) parts a channel which we are on.
Part.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Ping This method is called whenever we receive a PING request from another user.
Ping.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
PrivateMessage This method is called whenever a private message is sent to the PircBotX.
PrivateMessage.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Quit This method is called whenever someone (possibly us) quits from the server.
Quit.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
RemoveChannelBan Called when a hostmask ban is removed from a channel.
RemoveChannelBan.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
RemoveChannelKey Called when a channel key is removed.
RemoveChannelKey.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
RemoveChannelLimit Called when the user limit is removed for a channel.
RemoveChannelLimit.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
RemoveInviteOnly Called when a channel has 'invite only' removed.
RemoveInviteOnly.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
RemoveModerated Called when a channel has moderated mode removed.
RemoveModerated.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
RemoveNoExternalMessages Called when a channel is set to allow messages from any user, even if they are not actually in the channel.
RemoveNoExternalMessages.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
RemovePrivate Called when a channel is marked as not being in private mode.
RemovePrivate.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
RemoveSecret Called when a channel has 'secret' mode removed.
RemoveSecret.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
RemoveTopicProtection Called when topic protection is removed for a channel.
RemoveTopicProtection.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
ServerPing The actions to perform when a PING request comes from the server.
ServerPing.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
ServerResponse This is called when we receive a numeric response from the IRC server.
ServerResponse.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
SetChannelBan Called when a user (possibly us) gets banned from a channel.
SetChannelBan.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
SetChannelKey Called when a channel key is set.
SetChannelKey.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
SetChannelLimit Called when a user limit is set for a channel.
SetChannelLimit.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
SetInviteOnly Called when a channel is set to 'invite only' mode.
SetInviteOnly.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
SetModerated Called when a channel is set to 'moderated' mode.
SetModerated.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
SetNoExternalMessages Called when a channel is set to only allow messages from users that are in the channel.
SetNoExternalMessages.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
SetPrivate Called when a channel is marked as being in private mode.
SetPrivate.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
SetSecret Called when a channel is set to be in 'secret' mode.
SetSecret.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
SetTopicProtection Called when topic protection is enabled for a channel.
SetTopicProtection.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Time This method is called whenever we receive a TIME request.
Time.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Topic This method is called whenever a user sets the topic, or when PircBotX joins a new channel and discovers its topic.
Topic.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Unknown This method is called whenever we receive a line from the server that the PircBotX has not been programmed to recognise.
Unknown.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
UserList This method is called when we receive a user list from the server after joining a channel.
UserList.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
UserMode Called when the mode of a user is set.
UserMode.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Version This method is called whenever we receive a VERSION request.
Version.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
Voice Called when a user (possibly us) gets voice status granted in a channel.
Voice.Event Event that is passed to all listeners that contains all the given information.
